messageBody:
Jon:

I didn't get much sleep last night, and I just spent some time intending to
send a post to the Read Alphabet group -- the post being partially about my
frustrations with the Shavian site. With my current state of fatigue, my
new e-mail program and the auto-fill function switched on, I managed to
send the post to the Shavian site.

While I didn't really say anything bad about anybody, I am annoyed at being
such a doofus. It was a little more straightforward than I intended being
on that site. Oh well. If anybody is offended, I guess I'll hear about it.

Paige
